		<Nullable>enable</Nullable>

		<Version>2.0.0</Version>

		<Description>NewRelic NerdGraph log query backend for OutWit.Common.Logging.Query. Implements ILogQueryProvider over NRQL (search, statistics, distinct values, scroll-to-timestamp) and adds NewRelic-specific billing data via INewRelicProvider.</Description>
